\begin{Qtabular}{llll}
 /kpaga/ & [kpàɣà] &	have & v\\
   /doga/  & [dòɣà]	& Doga&  propn\\
/tʃaktʃak/ &	[tʃáɣətʃák] &		tattoo	& ono\\	
%/patʃɪgɪɪ/-/wɪɪla/ & [pàtʃɪ́gwɪ̀ɪ̀là]  & 	stomachache&  n\\
/vʊga/-/tɪɪna/ & [vʊ́ɣtɪ́ɪ́ná]	& priest &  n\\

\end{Qtabular} 
